left to right direction

'Interacción entre distintas clases'
AppCompatActivity <|-- MainActivity
AppCompatActivity <|-- HomeActivity

onClickListener <|.. HomeActivity
onClickListener <|.. MainActivity
AndroidViewModel <|-- UserListViewModel

Fragment <|-- UserListFragment
Fragment <|-- ConfigFragment
Fragment <|-- SupportFrament



ConnectionClient - LoginApiService: loginApiService >
ConnectionClient - AuthApiService: authApiService >
MainActivity - ConnectionClient: connectionClient >
HomeActivity . UserListFragment
HomeActivity . ConfigFragment
HomeActivity . SupportFragment
UserListFragment - UserListViewModel: userListViewModel >
UserListViewModel - UserListRepository: userListRepository >
UserListRepository - ConnectionClient: connectionClient >


'Declaración de las clases'
